spec.description: ClusterSyncLeaseSpec is the specification of a ClusterSyncLease.

renewTime.description: RenewTime is the time when SyncSets and SelectorSyncSets were last applied to the cluster.

exampleYAML:
apiVersion: hiveinternal.openshift.io/v1alpha1
kind: ClusterSyncLease
metadata:
  name: example-clustersynclease
  namespace: default
spec:
  renewTime: "example-renewTime"
